{"Title":"蒜香红薯叶的做法","Primary":["红薯叶300克"],"Auxiliary":["辣椒2根","蒜3粒","食盐4克","花生油3汤匙","白糖2克","酱油1汤匙"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.原料图","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_44390.jpg","2.去掉一些不要的叶子","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_53643.jpg","3.冲洗干净后，加盐浸泡10分钟","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_63823.jpg","4.蒜头剁碎，辣椒切小块","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_69270.jpg","5.下油锅，爆香蒜头","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_68277.jpg","6.倒进红薯叶","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_74422.jpg","7.加少许盐、糖进行调味","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_74682.jpg","8.再加少许酱油调味","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_14160.jpg","9.最后倒进辣椒一同翻炒至熟即可","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_58056.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_57870.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/59/199/2299809/n2299809_44054.jpg","烹饪技巧","　　不想吃太辣的，辣椒最后放，翻炒几下就可以。"]}